{
  "texts": [
    "94 This approach could provide a more solid foundation for evaluating consumer expectations of AI safety.",
    "The PLD Proposal also modifies the time point at which defectiveness is assessed for products that require software upgrades and updates.",
    "95 The PLD Proposal recognises that manufacturers retain control over digital products even after they have been introduced to the market.",
    "Producers may be obliged to upgrade existing products when more recent AI software increases safety.",
    "96 This acknowledges the ongoing responsibility of manufacturers in maintaining and updating the products."
  ]
}